snippet.title: JUMP Force - PS4/XB1/PC - Gameplay Mash-up (E3 2018)
snippet.description:
In case you missed all the gameplay sessions released so far for the ultimate cross-over JUMP FORCE, here is an overloaded mash-up of the Goku, Luffy, Naruto, Zoro and Sasuke’s best moves!
JUMP Force is coming to Xbox One, PlayStation 4 and PC in 2019!
